BOSCAN AND LL-652 OPERATING SERVICE AGREEMENTS IN VENEZUELA TO

EMPRESAS MIXTAS (I.E., JOINT STOCK CONTRACTUAL STRUCTURES), AND

THESE INTERESTS ARE ACCOUNTED FOR AS EQUITY AFFILIATES.

