BANGLADESH.

CHEVRON IS THE OPERATOR OF THREE ONSHORE

BLOCKS, WITH A 98 PERCENT INTEREST IN BLOCKS 12, 13

AND 14 AND OPERATOR OF BLOCK 7, IN WHICH THE COMPANY HOLDS

