INCLUDED IN THE $1,539 MILLION YEAR-END 2007 RESERVE BALANCE WERE REMEDIATION ACTIVITIES

OF 240 SITES FOR WHICH THE COMPANY HAD BEEN IDENTIFIED AS A POTENTIALLY RESPONSIBLE PARTY OR

