HAS APPROVED THE FOLLOWING PERCENTAGE ASSET-ALLOCATION RANGES: EQUITIES 4070, FIXED INCOME/CASH

2060, REAL ESTATE 015 AND OTHER 05. THE SIGNIFICANT INTERNATIONAL PENSION PLANS ALSO HAVE

